## Special Notes for Minecraft Mod Distributors:

- You are allowed to include this mod in modpacks, provided the modpack itself is distributed non-commercially.
- You are allowed to include this mod in your mod (via "jar-in-jar"), provided the mod itself is not sold separately or monetized directly.
- Any commercial distribution of this mod (outside of modpack use) requires the author's written permission.
- Forks and modified versions must retain this license and credit the original author.

