This license applies only to the original mod source code and assets provided in this repository.

You are free to create derivative works (e.g., other mods, add-ons, maps, videos, or tools inspired by or using this mod), and these derivative products are not required to adopt this license. You may choose any license for your derivative creations, as long as the original mod code/assets are not directly reused beyond what this license allows.

